'''信任，但要核实'''（{{lang-rus|Доверяй, но проверяй|links=no|r=Doveryay, no proveryay|p=dəvʲɪˈrʲæj no prəvʲɪˈrʲæj}}）是一句[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]][[押韻|押韵]]谚语。美国总统里根在接受美国学者的建议下，于[[冷战|冷战]]时期对[[苏联|苏联]]谈判[[核裁军|核裁军问题]]时曾多次使用<ref name="bartons">{{cite web|title='Trust, but verify': An untrustworthy political phrase|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/trust-but-verify-an-untrustworthy-political-phrase/2016/03/11/da32fb08-db3b-11e5-891a-4ed04f4213e8_story.html?noredirect=on|accessdate=25 June 2019|author=Barton Swaim|date=11 March 2016|newspaper=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204213456/https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/trust-but-verify-an-untrustworthy-political-phrase/2016/03/11/da32fb08-db3b-11e5-891a-4ed04f4213e8_story.html?noredirect=on}}</ref>。

